{"tid":513071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞典一年Working Holiday， 元旦日可申請","createTime":"2017-12-29T07:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T13:12:56.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"da84f52fec6b5727488b45505737b0f8e14c2547","tid":513071,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/29/151412_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F29%2F151412_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=34547cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">瑞典北部接近北極圈，有機會看到北極光</span><br />\n<br />\n港府宣佈，香港與瑞典雙邊工作假期計劃（Working Hoilday）將於明年元旦日起接受申請，18至30歲的香港青年只有符合既定要求即能到瑞典遊歷一年，瑞典人來港工作假期名額每年500個，但港人到瑞典工作假期的名額則不設上限！瑞典是目前與香港達成假期計劃安排的第12個國家。根據入境處網站資料，申請人必須提供不少於港幣2萬元的經濟證明、購買醫療、住院保健、遣返和責任保險。<br />\n<br />\n入境處指，申請人在當年一年期間，可選擇報讀為期不超過半年的進修或培訓課程，又或者選擇在當地工作賺取旅費，但不得為同一名僱主工作超過半年。有興趣的青年可聯絡入境處或透過其網站取得有關資料：<a href=\"http://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/visas/working_holiday_scheme.html#firstTab&amp;4&amp;note1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fservices%2Fvisas%2Fworking_holiday_scheme.html%23firstTab%264%26note1&d=HT%2BmosxtFQmebK13LlDiknIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=4bc4eb8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/visas/working_holiday_scheme.html#firstTab&amp;4&amp;note1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171229/57638871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171229%2F57638871&d=HT%2BmosxtFQmebK13LlDiknIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8e3c497d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171229%2F57638871&h=ac0f8570\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171229/57638871</a>"},{"pid":"d2d750e1565af8a4090822b2431cd3eedd3e540d","tid":513071,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:27:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"246e6bad254c4907bd23946c90bbd11ef983f6a8","tid":513071,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:09:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f46fe973832848a535d54e6aa0bfdda4aac585f2","tid":513071,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}